OL,6,FUK taxpayers have paid out more than
OL,7,F#34,000 to cover the costs of Science
OL,8,FSecretary Michelle Donelan's libel
OL,9,Fcase - more than double the original
OL,10,Fsum the government had admitted to.
OL,12,FThe Department for Science, Innovation
OL,13,Fand Technology confirmed last month it
OL,14,Fpaid #15,000 to settle the libel
OL,15,Faction brought by Professor Kate Sang,
OL,16,Fafter Ms Donelan wrongly accused her
OL,17,Fof supporting or expressing sympathy
OL,18,Ffor Hamas.
