OL,4,CMichelle Donelan's libel case
OL,6,FHowever, it has been revealed that an
OL,7,Fadditional #19,000 of taxpayers' money
OL,8,Fwas used to cover the legal costs.
OL,10,FIn a letter to Labour's shadow science
OL,11,Fsecretary Peter Kyle, the Science
OL,12,FDepartment's permanent secretary Sarah
OL,13,FMunby admitted the full cost was more
OL,14,Fthan twice the figure the department
OL,15,Fhad admitted to, with another #19,385
OL,16,Fspent on legal costs.
