OL,6,FMs Munby said the taxpayer had covered
OL,7,Fthe costs as ministers were
OL,8,Findemnified for "things done or
OL,9,Fdecisions made in the course of their
OL,10,Fministerial duties".
OL,12,FThe figure includes #7,785 of costs
OL,13,Fincurred by the Government Legal
OL,14,FDepartment and another #11,600 spent
OL,15,Fon external counsel, with neither
OL,16,Ffigure including VAT.
