OL,4,CMichelle Donelan's libel case
OL,6,FBut the full bill for the taxpayer
OL,7,Fcould be even higher once the costs of
OL,8,Fa separate investigation by UK
OL,9,FResearch and Innovation (UKRI) are
OL,10,Ffactored in.
OL,12,FOpposition figures have called for Ms
OL,13,FDonelan to pay back the money herself.
OL,15,FMr Kyle said the fact taxpayers were
OL,16,Fpicking up the bill was "a slap in the
OL,17,Fface to hardworking families", adding
OL,18,Fthe money had been "wasted on
OL,19,Funprofessional and libelous behaviour
OL,20,Ffrom a Conservative cabinet minister".
