OL,6,FThe letter followed a tweet by Prof
OL,7,FSang saying "This is disturbing", and
OL,8,Fcontaining a link to an article by the
OL,9,FGuardian newspaper describing the
OL,10,Fresponse to the Hamas attacks in the
OL,11,FUK, while Dr Patel had retweeted a
OL,12,Fpost describing Israeli actions as
OL,13,F"genocide and apartheid".
OL,15,FMs Donelan's intervention triggered an
OL,16,Finvestigation by UKRI, which had
OL,17,Fappointed the academics to its
OL,18,Fadvisory group on equality, diversity
OL,19,Fand inclusion (EDI).
