OL,6,FDetails obtained under freedom of
OL,7,Finformation rules by website Research
OL,8,FProfessional News found the UKRI
OL,9,Finvestigation had cost #23,280,
OL,10,Fincluding VAT, putting the total cost
OL,11,Fto the taxpayer of Ms Donelan's letter
OL,12,Fat almost #60,000.
OL,14,FLast month, Ms Donelan accepted that
OL,15,FProf Sang's comments referred to the
OL,16,FGuardian story as a whole, and not
OL,17,Fjust the headline, which focused on
OL,18,Fthe government's crackdown on support
OL,19,Ffor Hamas.
